{
  "texts": [
    "In some cases, it has the capability to handle enormous amounts of data for validation.",
    "Yet, these mechanisms face interpretability-based issues as they have limited interpretability ranges and poor efficiency in the sequential information.",
    "Furthermore, the training procedures require more time.",
    "Thus, resolving multiple limitations presented in the conventional CNN technique is important to provide accurate motion intention predicted outcomes.",
    "Thus, the LSTM mechanism is introduced in the research work to predict human motion intentions accurately, and the jointly developed version is named AH-CNN-LSTM."
  ]
}